## Package manager

Toujours utiliser **pnpm** :
- `pnpm create adonisjs@latest my-app`
- `pnpm install`, `pnpm build`, `pnpm dev`
- `pnpm install --prod` (production)
- `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` (CI)

