## Routing & Controllers

### Barrel controllers (v7)
```typescript
// start/routes.ts
import { controllers } from '#generated/controllers'

// Routes auto-nommées : posts.index, posts.show, posts.store...
router.get('/posts', [controllers.Posts, 'index'])
router.get('/posts/:id', [controllers.Posts, 'show'])
router.post('/posts', [controllers.Posts, 'store'])
router.put('/posts/:id', [controllers.Posts, 'update'])
router.delete('/posts/:id', [controllers.Posts, 'destroy'])
```

Le barrel `#generated/controllers` est auto-généré dans `.adonisjs/server/controllers.ts` par le dev server. Même pattern pour les events et policies.

### URL type-safe
```typescript
import { urlFor } from '@adonisjs/core/services/url_builder'
const url = urlFor('posts.show', { id: post.id })
// ❌ Erreur TypeScript si route inexistante ou params incorrects
```

