## Déploiement (points clés)

- Build : `pnpm build` → standalone JS dans `./build`
- CI : `NODE_ENV=development pnpm install` (devDeps nécessaires pour tsc/vite)
- Runtime : `NODE_ENV=production`
- Démarrage : `cd build && pnpm install --prod && node bin/server.js`
- Migrations : `node ace migration:run --force`
- Nginx : ajouter `keepAliveTimeout: 55000` dans `config/app.ts`

### Dockerfile
```dockerfile
FROM node:lts-bookworm-slim AS base
RUN npm install -g pnpm

FROM base AS deps
WORKDIR /app
COPY package.json pnpm-lock.yaml ./
RUN pnpm install --frozen-lockfile

FROM deps AS build
WORKDIR /app
COPY . .
RUN node ace build

FROM base AS production
WORKDIR /app
ENV NODE_ENV=production
COPY --from=build /app/build ./
RUN pnpm install --prod
EXPOSE 3333
CMD ["node", "bin/server.js"]
```

